      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This specimen is mechanically flawless, boasting a crisp Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains structurally superior with proactive subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry. All critical maintenance\u2014including the VANOS system overhaul and rod bearing replacement\u2014has been executed to exacting standards, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency and rotational balance. The paint-metered exterior and pristine cabin reflect a lifetime of climate-controlled storage. This is a turn-key example of high-revving atmospheric performance.",
